{"tid":1442760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角之戰意義","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:57.000Z","uid":244509,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9273de2bb936203c2d341bd1b1e38c9dd9b6b9ea","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"大勝:<br />\n- 重傷國內打手, 令其他同鄉不敢來港<br />\n- 中共動員黑幫維穩手段失敗, 只剩下解放軍<br />\n<br />\n大敗:<br />\n- 市民埋下心理恐懼, 不敢遊行 (但機場集會, 擺工仍可舉行)<br />\n- 勇武派重創(游擊戰仍可持續, 但出於恐懼可能停止)<br />\n- 中共恐嚇繼續動員黑幫<br />\n- 黑警繼續被傳媒追擊(如果選擇戰, 唔好圍警署同set roadblock, 等佢無藉口失踪)<br />\n<br />\n不分勝負(小勝, 小敗)<br />\n- 中共繼續動員黑幫, 打消耗戰<br />\n<br />\n回避(遇事即逃):<br />\n- 探清虛實, 了解中共動員能力<br />\n- 中共繼續動員黑幫"},{"pid":"d18c367ab0e7c3b99d79bbd517d287559bfb16d8","tid":1442760,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c144c14636fc657cafd46550ecadcc98c050e92","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實今個星期可以先迴避, 搵街坊探清虛實, 安全至上"},{"pid":"87246dd7244664994750d1d8358385c82c3982d0","tid":1442760,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"唔好阻人去邊"},{"pid":"2935edf28716bd93aeff8da43d6982c8a5a1cd9e","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87246dd7244664994750d1d8358385c82c3982d0","tid":1442760,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"唔好阻人去邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"正常打仗前都要收咗風先:<br />\n- 敵軍有幾多人<br />\n- 用咩武器"},{"pid":"b49022a013d39cdba25d82087ea805a3f21c6d0b","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"如果今日由於情報不足, 導致大敗, 輸一鋪可能就輸哂<br />\n<br />\n各位勇武派堅持要去既話, 記得唔好咁快上裝, 保持低調, 行幾個圈睇下對家咩料先, 未圍警署可以報警, 收走佢地d武器先<br />\n<br />\n人數, 裝備佔優 &gt; roadblock &gt; 戰<br />\n相反緊係散水"},{"pid":"8d524b7b81f67db6544962a88acc2ac78fccb392","tid":1442760,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:21:03.000Z","msg":"小心打完勁多狗黎收頭，捉黑衫"},{"pid":"a4825f3a414a9f6318b9491a35f3c6c20bf9a239","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"切忌被引入橫行窄巷伏擊, 留係大街充份利用人數優勢"},{"pid":"efa67beb6e61e3a9dba4ee1147495ff086e6a6d0","tid":1442760,"uid":31244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"13:13 <br />\n現在北角每個街口都有警察x 10左右，在英皇道，新都城有福建佬5件，富臨4件，每條街都有1至2個睇水。無意聽到其中一個說，就坐在此等人來，其中一個答要6至8才可打"},{"pid":"3c856dd0038cc3cd85d1dbbde64934b3b27e986f","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"［街坊資訊］北角探子報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f0a71fd97e2996055e113e8cf3173241f81f2b15","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"［街坊資訊］北角探子報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"95be377b00b992b4e179b79e741329d66854810e","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"北角福建狗已準備高空擲物<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442898/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442898/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1107747729381260/posts/1385555021600528?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1107747729381260%2Fposts%2F1385555021600528%3Fsfns%3D1&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=1125a91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1107747729381260/posts/1385555021600528?sfns=1</a><br />\n［福建同鄉會打到黎］<br />\n8月11日：網絡流傳福建同鄉會長今日會血洗北角，有市民發現自己所住物業天台門無故俾刑毀，更放置10多箱空啤酒樽，似乎想當遊行市民到達北角時高空擲物！"},{"pid":"1f7aa2d8d5329a5829d31bbc05030666a5baa420","tid":1442760,"uid":244369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"北角已經十幾架車，很强狗力。 近JavaRoad"},{"pid":"8b79931a78d7c7efdf56e23fad53d5c669a5a7b0","tid":1442760,"uid":283525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"打贏:暴徒摳打遊客。打輸:愛國力量痛摳暴徒。邊個結果好Ｄ？"},{"pid":"d23b742131168812391099404de9dc56c433b305","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b79931a78d7c7efdf56e23fad53d5c669a5a7b0","tid":1442760,"uid":283525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"打贏:暴徒摳打遊客。打輸:愛國力量痛摳暴徒。邊個結果好Ｄ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"遊咩Q客ar, 搵鬼信咩"},{"pid":"8cf0abac2b549bad1d12c69bc88f982c8a9d99d1","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"［街坊資訊］北角探子報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"72a241aa55af563ea1176a81dc7cac242ae403a3","tid":1442760,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n之前追蹤D 3毛全部都叫我地去北角<br />\n今日北角一定要空城計,<br />\n等佢比錢請人黎無目標打，<br />\n邊個吹雞去北角 <br />\n一係鬼一係on9</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f3789036938f86261abb912720fbbe57b0415d2","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a241aa55af563ea1176a81dc7cac242ae403a3","tid":1442760,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n之前追蹤D 3毛全部都叫我地去北角<br />\n今日北角一定要空城計,<br />\n等佢比錢請人黎無目標打，<br />\n邊個吹雞去北角 <br />\n一係鬼一係on9</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"警察出哂黎企街, 其實唔會打得成, 放心"},{"pid":"338b022f4a7ba1d01547cb030a755285f9bf272e","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:52:08.000Z","msg":"［街坊資訊］北角探子報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441272/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n北角福建狗已準備高空擲物<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442898/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442898/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1107747729381260/posts/1385555021600528?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1107747729381260%2Fposts%2F1385555021600528%3Fsfns%3D1&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=1125a91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1107747729381260/posts/1385555021600528?sfns=1</a><br />\n［福建同鄉會打到黎］<br />\n8月11日：網絡流傳福建同鄉會長今日會血洗北角，有市民發現自己所住物業天台門無故俾刑毀，更放置10多箱空啤酒樽，似乎想當遊行市民到達北角時高空擲物！"},{"pid":"1ae79053c39684be57f6e2a927d50bdc02ea3c5e","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:01:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果live見到英皇道港鐵出口廢老掛國旗, 軍裝企隔離<br />\n唔知精兵收埋係邊"},{"pid":"21b2c06124b4ca7f1b72575c9b693a0c16984af8","tid":1442760,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c144c14636fc657cafd46550ecadcc98c050e92","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實今個星期可以先迴避, 搵街坊探清虛實, 安全至上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"天琦：<br />\n//<span style=\"color: gold;\">但我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們必須警惕每一言一行，到底會更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？<br />\n<br />\n當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，<span style=\"color: gold;\">我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。</span><br />\n<br />\n我衷心祈求每個香港人都能夠平安渡過這個歷史關口。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天琦一句好過我講十句.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">與其將福建佬當敵人 倒不如將佢地變成敵人的敵人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2823021cf10a332033b976f7246ac5ab5318313e","tid":1442760,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KPRLP3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKPRLP3M.jpg&h=8d2ef63d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03d7de4287f74cfb5bc83e7f4a3dfdf5f2442e61","tid":1442760,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：「和你飛」&bull;入機場（1300）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月11日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"}]}